Version 0.4
-------------
* support  Mark6 units with more than 4 slots
* properly determine position of disks on the SAS controller bus independently from controller manufacturer logic
* controller identification by PCI bus ID to preserve mounting logic through machine reboots
* Version for DiFX-2.9

Version 0.3
-----------
* Post DiFX-2.6
* ignore non-SAS hotplug add events, such as USB hotplug device
* Version for DiFX-2.8

Version 0.2
-----------
* Post DiFX-2.5
* Version for DiFX-2.6, Mar 4, 2019

Version 0.1
-----------
* Initial version
* Version for DiFX-2.5, May 16, 2017
